## Form Rules

- Use react-hook-form for form state management and validation
- Use zod for schema validation and type inference
- Implement proper error handling and user feedback
- Use controlled components for complex form interactions
- Separate zod schemas into dedicated files in a schemas/ directory
    - Each form/feature should have its own schema file
    - Example structure: _schemas/auth.schema.ts, _schemas/profile.schema.ts
    - Export both the schema and inferred TypeScript type: z.infer<typeof formSchema>
    - Keep schemas modular and reusable across components
